data.description:
Step right into this incredible 2800 square foot home, the dream destination for your, happy family! Imagine the space, comfort, and a treasure trove of attractive features waiting just for you. As you approach, those double front entry doors? They're like a warm, stylish hug, welcoming you home with elegance and charm that's truly irresistible.
And once you're inside, you're in for a treat! The hardwood floors, they wrap you up in cozy vibes, making you feel right at home.  The travertine tiles? They're the perfect mix of class and practicality, adding a dash of sophistication to your daily life It's a prime Location! Your new home, backs onto a serene, scenic preserve, your very own private paradise in your backyard, family gatherings, barbecues, and lazy afternoons.. The master suite, it's the crown jewel of this home. Imagine having a spacious, peaceful retreat where you can relax and recharge after a long day of family fun. Walk a few steps, you'll discover the spacious master bath, complete with all the modern amenities you could wish for. A soaking tub for those much-needed "me time" moments, a separate walk-in shower, and double sinks for those busy mornings. '||chr(10)||'In a nutshell, this home is the ultimate blend of comfort, elegance, and convenience - it's got everything a big family like yours needs. Plus, there's a 3-car garage, so your vehicles and outdoor gear have a cozy spot to call home, too.'||chr(10)||'So, what are you waiting for? Your new adventure in family living awaits. Come on in and make it yours!'||chr(10)||'
